data.description: Charming 3 Bed, 2 Bath, over 1,700 square foot home in Clinton Twp with many updates including kitchen and baths.   If you love to entertain or being a chef this kitchen has the space and open concept for what you are looking for.  Wood floors throughout the kitchen and dining areas.  Family room has an outstanding center point fireplace and new carpet.  The primary bedroom is located on the other side of the house with an updated primary bath.  Two other bedrooms are spacious and located on the other side of the house.  Updated bath with jetted tub.  Talking about relaxing in the summers enjoying this oversized deck and watch the kids or dogs play in the full fenced backyard.  Located near just about everything you want to do - hike, walk dogs, canoe, Metro Park, beach, highways and much more.  L'Anse Creuse Schools District.
